<p></p>
<h1 id=3D"MentorlinkAppProductRequirements-1.Introduction">1. Introduction&=
nbsp;</h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>This document describes the required functionality of the Mentorlink app=
. It is expected that various features of the app will be developed in phas=
es, so where appropriate the phases are mentioned along with the requiremen=
ts.&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Mentorlink app will be mobile app only. HTML5 app will be developed firs=
t, followed by the native iPhone app and the native android app. iPad app o=
r other types (Alexa app/skill, desktop app etc.) are out of the scope of t=
his document.&nbsp;</p>
<p></p>
<h1 id=3D"MentorlinkAppProductRequirements-2.UI/UX">2. UI/UX&nbsp;</h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Please see the mock-ups in the Appendix Section.&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"27603e78-00ad-4671-9f9d-ed5=
faef8bbd7" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 69.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 88.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 310.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 95.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 118.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Req No.&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Category&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Description&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Priority&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Readiness and Plan</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sign-On&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Users will be required to sign-on using an=20
<del>email address,</del> or phone number, or apple, google,=20
<del>or linked-in accounts&nbsp;</del></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-2&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sign-On&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>
<del>When using email address, users will be required to create a secure pa=
ssword (requirement similar to gmail)&nbsp;</del></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>n/a. Not considered for Mentorlink Next</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-3&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sign-On&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>When using phone numbers, no password will be needed, instead an authent=
ication code (6-digit text) will be sent to the registered phone number. Au=
thentication code will suffice as the passcode&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-4&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sign-On&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3<sup>rd</sup> Party authentication (apple or google; not sure if linked=
-in allows this) will suffice for the user to login&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-4.1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sign-On/EULA&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>EULA will be shown to user at the time of sign-on. Check compliance on t=
he data collection.&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-5&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sign-On and Sign-Off&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Users will not have to sign-on again unless they explicitly sign-off&nbs=
p;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-6&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sign-On and Sign-Off&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sign-on information is deleted when the app is deleted from the phone&nb=
sp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-7&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sign-on Profile Page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Users will be shown the Profile page which will ask linked-in profile an=
d career interests. After the first sign-on, Profile page will be shown onl=
y when users click on the Profile icon&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-8&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Home Page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>For subsequent sign-ons, users will be shown a Front Page by default. Fe=
ed page will have 3 parts.&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-9&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Home Page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Top part will have a Search bar. Search bar will always be present. Plea=
se see the details on the Search bar in the Core Functionality section&nbsp=
;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-10&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Home Page&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Middle part will be scrollable and will show either feeds or chats from =
the contacts or groups. Please see the details on the Feed and Chats in the=
 Core Functionality section.&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-11&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Home Page&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Bottom part will have Profile, Feed (exact name TBD), Chat, Camera and S=
etting icons&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-12&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile Page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The Profile icon will be similar to the =E2=80=9CStatus=E2=80=9D icon on=
 WhatsApp&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-13&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile Page&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile page enables user to add/modify interests and skills, and see sa=
ved feeds. A separate page will pop up for the interests and skills. Profil=
e page will also have an upload photo option and an edit button (to add/del=
ete/modify =E2=80=9Cabout=E2=80=9D information)&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-13.1</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile Page/Mentor signup option</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile page will check with users if they would like to volunteer for m=
entoring others. If they check =E2=80=9Cyes=E2=80=9D then there will be sma=
ll (m) will show on their name. Removing the =E2=80=9Cyes=E2=80=9D will aut=
omatically delete the list of mentees (see UX-13.2)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>To be considered for Mentorlink Next</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-13.2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile Page/Mentees</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>If this user is a mentor, the profile page will show a list of mentees</=
p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>To be considered for Mentorlink Next</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-13.3</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile Page/Mentors</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>If this user has mentors on the Mentorlink, the profile page will show a=
 list of mentors</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>To be considered for Mentorlink Next</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-14&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile/Saved Feeds Page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Saved Feeds will show saved feeds in the order of the timestamp. Users w=
ill be able archive or unsave the feeds with a swipe (left and right swipe =
respectively)&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-15&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile/Recent Updates&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Users will be able to see Recent Profile Updates (career summary and not=
 interests) of their contacts on the Profile page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P2&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-16&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile/Recent Updates&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Recent Updates will be limited to 5 updates at any time. Once seen, a re=
cent update will not be shown. Recent Updates will follow certain algorithm=
 (e.g., sorted on &lt;most contacted, most recent&gt;)&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P2&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-16&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile/Muted Updates&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>
<del>Muted Updates will be available as well. There will be an expand butto=
n that the user can see to see the Muted Updates&nbsp;</del></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P2&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>n/a. Not considered for Mentorlink Next</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-18&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Setting Page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Following settings will be available on the Setting Page. 1. Account 2. =
Help 3. Tell a Friend 4. Notifications 5. Storage and Data 6. About&nbsp;</=
p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-19&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Setting/Account Page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Account Page will have Change Password, Privacy, Two-Step Verification, =
Delete My Account&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-20&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Account/Privacy Page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>
<del>Privacy Page will show options whether to show or limit Profile Page u=
pdates to the contacts&nbsp;</del></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>n/a. Not considered for Mentorlink Next</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-21&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Account/Change Password&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>This Page will enable changing the password for the user&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-22&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Account/&lt;Other&gt; Page&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>All the links from the Account Page will be common sense (e.g., Two step=
 verification will allow 2-step verification)&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P2&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-23&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Setting/Help Page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Help Page will show Contact Us, Help Center&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-24&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Setting/Tell a Friend Page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Tell a Friend page will allow a user to invite their friends either by p=
hone# or by email address&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P1&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-25&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Setting/About Page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>About Page will link to <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://Mentor=
link.ai" rel=3D"nofollow">Mentorlink.ai</a>=E2=80=99s Web Page {which will =
be a minimal page}&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P2&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-26&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Setting/&lt;Other&gt; Page&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Notification Page will present notification choices to the user; Storage=
 and Data Page will similarly show Storage and Data choices to the user {Ba=
nner, ...}. Feed and Chat notifications will be handled on the Feed and Cha=
t Pages in the next section&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P3&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>To be considered for Mentorlink Next</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>
<del>UX-27</del>&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>
<del>Camera</del>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>(Note: Camera is part of the Chat Page. See CF-27)</em>&nbsp;</p></t=
d>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>
<del>Users will be able to upload pictures using the camera of their device=
</del>&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>
<del>P1</del>&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-28&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Profile/Camera&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Users will be able to upload videos (of events etc.) using the camera of=
 their device&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P2&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>n/a. Not considered for Mentorlink Next</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-29&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sign-On, Multiple devices&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Users may have signed on with multiple devices. Each device will continu=
e to work with its own state&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P2&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UX-30&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Multiple devices will only be in the same state only after they are all =
idle&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>P2&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3.1 (6)</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
